B4%E6%8C%87%E5%BF%83%E6%80%A7/</link><pubDate>Sat, 21 May 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Sat, 21 May 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E8%97%8F%E4%BC%A0/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%86%E6%BB%A1%E7%9B%B4%E6%8C%87%E5%BF%83%E6%80%A7/</guid><description>全知麦彭仁波切 造 上师妙吉祥智慧勇士前敬礼！ 不必广闻深思及磨炼，唯以窍诀之宗护心性， 城中众多咒士虽不勤，速诣持明地即深道力。 彼亦，自心不思一切</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>心性</category><category>大圆满</category><category>大圆满直指心性</category><category>全知麦彭仁波切</category><category>佛</category><category>藏传</category></item><item><title>圆觉经摘要</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/reading/%E5%9C%86%E8%A7%89%E7%BB%8F%E6%91%98%E8%A6%81/</link><pubDate>Mon, 02 May 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Mon, 02 May 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/reading/%E5%9C%86%E8%A7%89%E7%BB%8F%E6%91%98%E8%A6%81/</guid><description>极简概述 1 正见（智慧）：了达无明，了达空 details 2 知幻即离，离幻即觉 details 3 正念（思维住持）：无身，无心，（觉性平等不动）无修无证 details 4 断轮回根本：心为</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>心性</category><category>圆觉经</category><category>摘要</category><category>佛</category><category>禅宗</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>道德经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>摘要 道可道，非常道；名可名，非常名。无名天地之始，有名万物之母。 是以圣人处无为之事，行不言之教，万物作焉而不辞，生而不有，为而不恃，功成而弗</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>道德经</category><category>心性</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>道德经-马王堆帛书版</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E7%BB%8F-%E9%A9%AC%E7%8E%8B%E5%A0%86%E5%B8%9B%E4%B9%A6%E7%89%88/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E7%BB%8F-%E9%A9%AC%E7%8E%8B%E5%A0%86%E5%B8%9B%E4%B9%A6%E7%89%88/</guid><description>01 道可道也，非恒道也。名可名也，非恒名也。无名万物之始也，有名万物之母也。故：恒无欲也，以观其眇；恒有欲也，以观其徼。两者同出，异名同谓。玄</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>道德经</category><category>心性</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>道德经-浙江道教协会</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E7%BB%8F-%E6%B5%99%E6%B1%9F%E9%81%93%E6%95%99%E5%8D%8F%E4%BC%9A/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E7%BB%8F-%E6%B5%99%E6%B1%9F%E9%81%93%E6%95%99%E5%8D%8F%E4%BC%9A/</guid><description>01.道可道，非常道。名可名，非常名。无名天地之始。有名万物之母。故常无欲以观其妙。常有欲以观 其徼。此两者同出而异名，同谓之玄。玄之又玄，众</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>道德经</category><category>心性</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>列子</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%88%97%E5%AD%90/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%88%97%E5%AD%90/</guid><description>摘要 正文 Ref 列子故事 列子文 列子文</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>列子</category><category>冲虚经</category><category>心性</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>牧牛图颂</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E7%A6%85%E5%AE%97/%E7%89%A7%E7%89%9B%E5%9B%BE%E9%A2%82/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E7%A6%85%E5%AE%97/%E7%89%A7%E7%89%9B%E5%9B%BE%E9%A2%82/</guid><description>著者：普明禅师(生卒年不详)，一说为北宋禅师，住持于龙泉寺。 怎么来认识我们这些烦恼呢？过去禅宗的祖师把我们的烦恼比喻成牛——牧牛、放牛，所以</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>心性</category><category>佛</category><category>公案</category><category>禅宗</category></item><item><title>十牛图</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E7%A6%85%E5%AE%97/%E5%8D%81%E7%89%9B%E5%9B%BE/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E7%A6%85%E5%AE%97/%E5%8D%81%E7%89%9B%E5%9B%BE/</guid><description>十二世纪，廓庵禅师著了一本名为《十牛图》的书，成为禅门中的至宝。他绘制了禅宗的《十牛图》，并以诗偈和散文加以评唱，形象地展现了由修行到证悟的</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>心性</category><category>佛</category><category>公案</category><category>禅宗</category></item><item><title>庄子</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%BA%84%E5%AD%90/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Sun, 10 Apr 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%BA%84%E5%AD%90/</guid><description>摘要 故事 Ref 庄子</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>庄子</category><category>心性</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>洞玄灵宝定观经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%AE%9A%E8%A7%82%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%AE%9A%E8%A7%82%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>诵读 天尊告左玄真人曰：夫欲修道，先能舍事。 外事都绝，无与忤心。然后安坐，内观心起。若觉一念起，须除灭, 务令安静。 其次，虽非的有贪着，浮游乱想</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>心性</category><category>早晚课</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>黄帝阴符经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%BB%84%E5%B8%9D%E9%98%B4%E7%AC%A6%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E9%BB%84%E5%B8%9D%E9%98%B4%E7%AC%A6%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>上篇 观天之道，执天之行，尽矣。故天有五贼，见之者昌。五贼在心，施行于天。宇宙在乎手，万化生乎身。天性，人也；人心，机也。立天之道，以定人也。</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>阴符经</category><category>早晚课</category><category>心性</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>金刚经摘要</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E4%BD%9B/%E9%87%91%E5%88%9A%E7%BB%8F-%E6%91%98%E8%A6%81/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E4%BD%9B/%E9%87%91%E5%88%9A%E7%BB%8F-%E6%91%98%E8%A6%81/</guid><description>摘要 第一品 法会因由分 第二品 善现启请分 云何应住，云何降伏其心 第三品 大乘正宗分 如是灭度无量无数无边众生,实无众生得灭度者, 若菩萨有我相,人相,众</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>金刚经</category><category>心性</category><category>摘要</category><category>佛</category></item><item><title>太上老君说常清静经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E6%B8%85%E9%9D%99%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E6%B8%85%E9%9D%99%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>老君曰：大道无形，生育天地；大道无情，运行日月；大道无名，长养万物；吾不知其名，强名曰道。夫道者：有清有浊，有动有静；天清地浊，天动地静；男</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>清静经</category><category>心性</category><category>早晚课</category><category>炁體源流</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item><item><title>太上升玄消灾护命妙经</title><link>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%A4%AA%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87%E7%8E%84%E6%B6%88%E7%81%BE%E6%8A%A4%E5%91%BD%E5%A6%99%E7%BB%8F/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><atom:modified>Wed, 23 Feb 2022 00:00:00 +0000</atom:modified><guid>https://siteofen.github.io/zh/%E9%81%93/%E5%A4%AA%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87%E7%8E%84%E6%B6%88%E7%81%BE%E6%8A%A4%E5%91%BD%E5%A6%99%E7%BB%8F/</guid><description>尔时，元始天尊在七宝林中，五明宫内，与无极圣众，俱放无极光明，照无极世界，观无极众生，受无极苦恼；宛转世间，轮回生死，漂浪爱河，流吹欲海，沉</description><dc:creator>Om</dc:creator><category>早晚课</category><category>心性</category><category>道</category><category>经文</category></item></channel></rss>